Subject: [PATCH 4/8] =?UTF-8?q?fix(report=5Fcarbone):=20studio=20flicker?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20=E2=80=94=20skip=20re-entrant=20refresh=20tijdens=20load?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

De embedded studio verscheen kort en verdween direct. Oorzaak: een tweede
onWillLoadRoot/refreshStudio tijdens het ~2s openTemplate-window evalueerde
getIsCarboneReport() momentaan als false en riep handleHideStudio ->
setDisplayNone aan op de net-gemounte studio.

Guard: refreshStudio slaat een re-entrante refresh over zolang
isTemplateLoading actief is (self-clears na 2s of bij launchCarbone-return).
Vroege launchCarbone-return reset isTemplateLoading expliciet om guard-deadlock
te voorkomen.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 report_carbone/static/src/js/report/initiate_studio.js | 10 ++++++++++
 1 file changed, 10 insertions(+)

diff --git a/report_carbone/static/src/js/report/initiate_studio.js b/report_carbone/static/src/js/report/initiate_studio.js
index 87c8dfc..8714b6b 100644
--- a/report_carbone/static/src/js/report/initiate_studio.js
+++ b/report_carbone/static/src/js/report/initiate_studio.js
@@ -191,6 +191,15 @@ class CarboneStudioManager {
         return new Promise((resolve) => {
             this.debounceTimer = setTimeout(async () => {
                 try {
+                    // Skip re-entrant refresh while a template load is mid-flight
+                    // (the ~2s openTemplate window in safeOpenTemplate). A transient
+                    // re-render here re-evaluates getIsCarboneReport()=false and hides
+                    // the just-mounted studio ("appears then disappears" flicker).
+                    if (this.isTemplateLoading && this.currentStudio) {
+                        resolve();
+                        return;
+                    }
+
                     this.cleanup();
                     this.resetOptions();
 
@@ -269,6 +278,7 @@ class CarboneStudioManager {
     async launchCarbone(studio, studioURL, carboneToken) {
         if (!studio || !studioURL || !carboneToken) {
             DOMUtils.setDisplayNone(studio);
+            this.isTemplateLoading = false;   // niet vasthouden → refresh-guard deadlockt anders
             return false;
         }
 
